%h4 Most Improved Fantacy Palyers
- unless @improved_players.blank?
  %table{class: "table table-striped table-bordered table-condensed"}
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Palyer Id
        %th Player Name
        %th Slugging Percentage
    %tbody
      - @improved_players.each do |batting|
        %tr
          %td= batting.player_id
          %td= batting.player.name rescue ''
          %td= ''
